{"id": "1269343725012779141", "channel_id": "1266445653618327723", "type": 0, "author_id": "1046407805260812350", "author_name": "z1473", "author_bot": false, "content": "融災5-4\n拉蒙娜換成溫科爾\n利用溫科爾的爆發；\n以及利用「種子」，複製諾帝拉（2費）\n能加速艾爾瓦開啟超限\n\n心眼利刃「刻印推薦：鏡像」\n比起5回合才能進入超維空間\n鏡像後兩張手牌，反而比較好用\n\n\nhttps://youtu.be/SxfErXGlY5k?si=jX6Rda3HlQeVWrS6", "timestamp": "2024-08-03T17:18:47.309000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-08-03T17:30:03.381000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1269343724895342685", "filename": "1722704793826.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 142597, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1266445653618327723/1269343724895342685/1722704793826.jpg?ex=69cc01f7&is=69cab077&hm=7fbd721d4e44ba0c24da36483354eb372ae89e385e8cb51de52bdd3391f2786f&"}], "embeds": [{"type": "video", "title": "「忘卻前夜」融災5-4，超維盾擊", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SxfErXGlY5k", "description": ""}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1266445653618327723", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "盾擊之超維（奧爾拉篇）：", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1260133992636743681", "1174179755759763526"]}
